<h3>DNS</h3>
<p>DNS (Domain Name System) translates domain names into IP addresses, like a phonebook for the web.</p>

<h3>HTML</h3>
<p>HTML (Hyper Text Markup Language) structures web content using tags for headings, paragraphs, images, and links.</p>

